This option uses uses javax.servlet.ServletRequest.getRemoteAddr() method when calculating the remote address, and at this time, the address of the web server may be returned according to the web server settings.
At this time, the address used is delivered to HTTP header and this option is for using this value as the user address.

---

* Default value: None
* Type: string
* Sample value: X-REMOTE_ADDRESS
* Restart: Not required
* Supported version: 5.0.0